# 🚀 Task 01 - Responsive Landing Page

This project is part of my web development training with **SkillCraft Technology**. The goal was to design and build a **responsive landing page** with an interactive navigation menu that enhances the user experience.

---

## 🧩 Task Objective

- ✅ Build a responsive landing page layout.
- ✅ Create a navigation menu that:
  - Changes color or style on **scroll**.
  - Responds visually when **hovering** over menu items.
- ✅ Ensure the navigation bar is:
  - **Fixed at the top** of the page.
  - **Visible across all sections**.

---

## 💡 Key Learnings

Through this task, I enhanced my skills in:

- **HTML** & **CSS**: Structuring and styling responsive layouts.
- **JavaScript**: Adding dynamic behavior for scroll and hover interactions.
- **UI/UX Principles**: Building smooth and accessible user interfaces.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

